{"tid":1687064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驅使大家一直撐落去的並不是憤怒","createTime":"2019-11-01T14:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T23:21:46.000Z","uid":50457,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"70ef852ff180a5457f405a079efb0224e30f30a9","tid":1687064,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"而是良知<br />\n<br />\n良知話比你聽，無論再黑暗的日子，大家也會撐下去<br />\n<br />\n點解？<br />\n<br />\n唔係因為大家無野搵野嚟做。而係面對政府的醜陋，香港人的光輝，良知話比自己聽沒有理由點解要放棄<br />\n<br />\n香港人需要更加多的創意，遊行唔得就流水式集會，集會唔得就野餐，跑步，香港人從來唔會一成不變。<br />\n<br />\n多啲試唔同的方法，每人一步就更易成功<br />\n<br />\n為了逝去的義士，受重傷的手足，面臨上庭的兄弟，大家更需要用唔同的方法，全方位發動技能。<br />\n<br />\n禁制令係唔會禁止到香港人的良知，中共政府要為血腥鎮壓香港人付上慘痛的政治代價。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭要轉型升級，香港人重新集合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6352d76650f01e3f37e22a2e6ec52f9f3f3b83e","tid":1687064,"uid":172427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2d974f6840171eb100e2785ea9bac77ed86b73","tid":1687064,"uid":50457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"憤怒並不會提供永遠的推動力，但良知絕對有無窮無盡的力<br />\n<br />\n見到有人受傷，上前幫手<br />\n<br />\n見到有人被捕要錢打官司，會主動籌錢<br />\n<br />\n見到同學仔無錢食飯，會主動請佢食飯<br />\n<br />\n面對手足被殘酷對待，係良知話比你聽應該要憤怒<br 